THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS AND DATA
This restriction does not extend to third-party components and open data
used by the app, which remain under their own licences:
- MapLibre GL JS (vendor/) — BSD-3-Clause, (c) MapLibre contributors.
- Park connector & cycling path data — NParks "Park Connector Loop" and
