- Weather — NEA 2-hour forecast via data.gov.sg.
- Routing graph and Rail Corridor geometry (data/graph.json,
  data/rail.lines.geojson) — derived from OpenStreetMap,
  (c) OpenStreetMap contributors, and remain subject to the ODbL 1.0.
- Basemap tiles — OpenFreeMap; map data (c) OpenStreetMap contributors.

